#graphql

fragment VaultFields on Vault {
  debtToken
  apeDecimals
  debtSymbol
  collateralToken
  collateralSymbol
  vaultId
  leverageTier
  totalTea
  totalValue
  lockedLiquidity
  apeAddress
  taxAmount
  apeDecimals
  apeCollateral
  teaCollateral
  id
}

query VaultQuery($collateralToken: String, $debtToken: String, $leverageTier: Int, $lastId:String ) {
  vaults(
    orderDirection: desc
    first: 10
    orderBy: totalValue

  ) {
    ...VaultFields
  }
}
847baafaf71cab69f2034d36ea3d450625cbc642:
query getUserApePositions($user: Bytes) {
  userPositions(where: { user: $user }) {
    user
    vaultId
    APE
    balance
    debtToken
    debtSymbol
    positionDecimals
    collateralToken
    collateralSymbol
    leverageTier
  }
}
